<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg und Ulm</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Versucher die neuen Gulden deutlich minderwertiger einschätzen als diejenigen schwäbischer Währung, und rät den Adressaten, diese auch untersuchen zu lassen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_254" id="127r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_254_r2l21">Den von <expan>augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> . Vnd den von Vlme <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_254_r2l22"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verſüch<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbracht vnd ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l23">getan . vvıe daʒ etwıeuıl neẅer <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> her ʒu land <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein . den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l24">vaſt abgeſecʒt ſey vnd gar v̈bel beſteen gen den <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe man </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l25">nennet ſwebıſche <expan>weru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l26">als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> / auf das ob es eẅch geraten dunkt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_254_r2l27">daʒ Jr dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dıe ſıch der ſache <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / dıe <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> bey eẅch auch </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_255" id="127v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l2">mugt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſüchen</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_255_r1l1">daʒ ſıch eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> deſt bas darnach wıſſ ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> Vnd ob Jr darauf ıcht gedecht / daʒ eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l3">füklıch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vns ʒu <expan>verkund<ex>en</ex></expan> . Daʒ Jr vns das in guter <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_line_1576665255594_8218">auch <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet . als etc . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l6"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_254" id="127r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Augsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und den von Ulme
                                <expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>versüch<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        fürbracht und zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> getan, wie daz etwievil
                        newer <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> her zu land
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, den vast abgeseczt sey und gar übel
                        besteen gen den <expan>guld<ex>en,</ex></expan> die man nennet swebische
                                <expan>weru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>. Das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        guten <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> auf das, ob es ewch geraten dunkt,
                        daz ir die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n,</expan> die sich der sache
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, die <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        bey ewch auch <pb facs="#facs_255" id="127v"/>mugt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>süchen</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, <add>daz sich ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> dest bas darnach wiss zu
                                    <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan></add>; und ob ir darauf icht
                        gedecht, daz ewch füklich <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, uns zu
                                <expan>verkund<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir uns das in guter
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, als etc. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>. </ab>
</div>
